```java
// Determine which quadrant the mouse is in and position button accordingly
double centerX = screenWidth / 2;
double centerY = screenHeight / 2;

if (mouseX < centerX && mouseY < centerY) {
    // Top-left quadrant - position button in top-right area
    targetX = centerX + 50;
    targetY = margin;
} else if (mouseX >= centerX && mouseY < centerY) {
    // Top-right quadrant - position button in top-left area  
    targetX = centerX - buttonSize - 50;
    targetY = margin;
}
```
</augment_code_snippet>

