<augment_code_snippet path="src/ChatSidebar.java" mode="EXCERPT">
```java
// Position sidebar on opposite side of screen from mouse
boolean mouseInLeftHalf = mouseX < screenWidth / 2;

if (mouseInLeftHalf) {
    // Mouse on left side - position sidebar on right side
    targetX = screenWidth - sidebarWidth - margin;
} else {
    // Mouse on right side - position sidebar on left side
    targetX = margin;
}
```
</augment_code_snippet>

